View README for potential updates like docker, google cloud & SSO option

name: addms-by-example
description: Accelerated Domain-Driven Microservices might refer to an approach that aims to rapidly develop and deploy microservices-based systems while maintaining a strong focus on the business domain. A guide microservices evolutionary architecture thats fit to your reality

name: apexmq
description: ApexMQ - An open-source, developer-friendly library for integrating RabbitMQ with Django applications, designed to simplify message-based microservice architectures. ApexMQ offers intuitive decorators, signal-based model integration, and seamless message handling for robust, scalable systems.

name: cdc-standalone-listener
description: The CDC Standalone Listener is a lightweight tool designed to listen to database change events (inserts, updates, deletes) and process them in real-time. It can work independently without relying on heavy middleware and is suitable for microservice architectures, event-driven systems, and streaming data pipelines.
